author: Reuters Editorial
title: Fabrinet Reports Q2 Non-GAAP Earnings Per Share $0.72
text:
Feb 5 (Reuters) - Fabrinet:
* ANNOUNCES SECOND QUARTER FISCAL YEAR 2018 FINANCIAL RESULTS
* Q2 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.72 * Q2 GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.51 * SEES Q3 REVENUE $316 MILLION TO $324 MILLION * Q2 REVENUE $337.1 MILLION VERSUS $351.2 MILLION * SEES Q3 2018 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.70 TO $0.73 * SEES Q3 2018 GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.50 TO $0.53 * Q2 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.70, REVENUE VIEW $329.4 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* Q3 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.71, REVENUE VIEW $331.3 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon:
